		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Thanks Scott.  I don&#8217;t recall who famously said it, but &#8220;rules, once learnt, are meant to be broken&#8221;.  I practice Stu Hamm &amp; John Pattitucci 1FPF stretching exercises; the discipline helps me sight-read up-tempo walking bass lines, but for many grooves it&#8217;s just too uncomfortable.</p>
